Reuiqred GCC compiler to execute the code
Steps as given below

#1.	To compile the code for substition cipher
		$ gcc shift_cipher.c -o shift_cipher
	To Run the generated excutable
		$ ./shift_cipher

#2.	To compile the code for substition cipher
		$ gcc substitution_cipher.c -o subs
	To Run the generated excutable
		$ ./subs
